text: Andrea Dakó (born 12 August 1972) is a Hungarian badminton player, born in Budapest. She competed in women's singles and women's doubles at the 1992 Summer Olympics in Barcelona. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1972 births Category:Living people Category:Sportspeople from Budapest Category:Hungarian female badminton players Category:Olympic badminton players of Hungary Category:Badminton players at the 1992 Summer Olympics
